{
 "name": "RPlog_Simon_and_Satine",
 "title": "Simon and Satine",
 "summary": "Aboard her ship the Starfire, the surgeon Satine tends to her recovering patient, the Telgossian zealot Simon Sezirok, whose grievous wounds are healing at an astonishing, Force-accelerated rate. As Simon wakes clean-shaven and whole, the two fall into a probing philosophical exchange about the True Source, his self-described 'Selas' nature, and his crusade to purge the galaxy of Jedi and Sith. Satine challenges the futility of his solitary quest and suggests he found a school instead, but Simon insists his path ends only in death or victory. They discover common ground in their shared hatred of Palpatine -- whom Satine names as pure evil and the puppeteer behind the corrupted Jedi Jessalyn -- and Simon pledges to repay his debt by helping destroy him before Satine kisses his forehead and bids him rest.",
